I’ve been really enjoying the @indewild Eye Concentrate—I use it both day and night, though I tend to skip it in the daytime when I’m doing my makeup✨

There’s absolutely nothing wrong with the product; in fact, I love how it feels. But like with many skincare products, it’s not just what you use—it’s how you use it. Make sure you apply the right amount (a little goes a long way), and be consistent. 

I’m still in the early stages, so I’m excited to see how the results unfold!🌸
